doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset="utf-8")
    link(rel="shortcut icon", href="/favicon.ico")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no")
    meta(name="theme-color", content="#000000")
    title #{title}
    link(href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous")
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css")
    script(src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous")
    script(src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.12.9/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q" crossorigin="anonymous")
    script(src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl" crossorigin="anonymous")
    script(src="/js/custom.js")
  body
    div#root.thankyou-page
        div#quix-important-message
            span.quix-important-message Hi ScreenGenius user! We have just updated the tool to Version 3.1.1 for better experience and usability. Thanks for your support.
        div.header_section
            div.container.top_container
                header.ScreenGenius-header
                    nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-light
                        div.container-fluid
                            a.navbar-brand(href="/")
                                img(src="images/home/logo.png"  height="80" alt="CoolBrand")
                div.container-fluid
                    div.row
                        div.star_emoji
                            span.thankEmoji
                                span.emoji
                                    img(src="images/home/thankyouemoji.png")
                                    span.emoji_content
                                    h5 For choosing ScreenGenius
                                    p Buckle up! Your journey to create stunning masterpieces begins now.
        div.container-fluid.screen_recording_game
            div.container
                div.row
                    div.section_title
                        h1 To easily access ScreenGenius. Do this first.
                        p Follow the instructions for a seamless screenshotting experience!
                    div.col-lg-12.conversations-mid.extension_screen
                        div.ext_screen_1.exten_screen
                            span
                                h5 01
                                p Access ScreenGenius from Extensions menu.
                            span
                                img(src="images/home/extenstion_screen1.png")
                        div.ext_screen_1.exten_screen
                            span
                                h5 02
                                p Pin it to the bar.
                            span
                                img(src="images/home/ext_screen_2.png")
                        div.ext_screen_1.exten_screen
                            span
                                h5 03
                                p Start with selecting Screenshot or Screen recording mode.
                            span
                                img(src="images/home/ext_screen_3.jpg")
        div.container.screen_recording_game
            div.row
                div.section_title
                    h1 Ready for your first ScreenGenius screenshot?.
                    p Here's how you take your first capture.
                div.col-lg-12.conversations-mid.extension_screen
                    div.ext_screen_2.exten_screen
                        span
                            h5 01
                            p To take your first amazing screenshot, simply select the area you want to capture & ScreenGenius will do the rest.
                        span
                            img(src="images/home/ext_screen_4.png")
                    div.ext_screen_2.exten_screen
                        span
                            h5 02
                            p Now, edit it or annotate on it, to give your personalized touch.
                        span
                            img(src="images/home/ext_screen_5.png")
                    div.ext_screen_2.exten_screen
                        span
                            h5 03
                            p And now, it's ready to share via a shareable link or through an email.
                        span
                            img(src="images/home/ext_screen_6.png")
        div.container-fluid.screen_recording_game
            div.container
                div.row
                    div.section_title
                        h1 Screen recording made easy with ScreenGenius.
                        p And, now do your first screen recording with ScreenGenius like this.
                    div.col-lg-12.conversations-mid.extension_screen
                        div.ext_screen_3.exten_screen
                            span
                                h5 01
                                p Do your first screen recording by selecting your current window, or select all windows, your current tab or your camera.  
                            span
                                img(src="images/home/ext_screen_7.png")
                        div.ext_screen_3.exten_screen
                            span
                                h5 02
                                p Now, add text, effects, music and trim as you edit, with your creative genius hat on!
                            span
                                img(src="images/home/ext_screen_8.png")
                        div.ext_screen_3.exten_screen
                            span
                                h5 03
                                p Now it's ready to share via a sharing link with your friends. You can also upload the screen recordings on to the cloud easily.
                            span
                                img(src="images/home/ext_screen_9.png")
        div.footer
            div.container
                div.row
                    div.col-lg-4
                        span
                            img(src="images/home/footer-logo.png").sitetitle
                            p 
                                span Screenshots & Screen recordings 
                                span with a dash of your unique personality.
                    div.col-lg-4
                        span
                            ul
                                li 
                                    a(href="#") About us
                                li 
                                    a(href="#") Feedback
                                li 
                                    a(href="#") Privacy
                    div.col-lg-4
                        span
                            h5 Contact us
                            p Please contact us at the given email address. We will get back to you within 24 hours.
                            p 
                                a(mailto="support@screengenius.io") support@screengenius.io
                    div.social_icon_copy_right
                        div.row
                            div.col-lg-4
                                span 
                                    img(src="images/home/facebook.png")
                                span 
                                    img(src="images/home/instagram.png")
                                span 
                                    img(src="images/home/twitter.png")
                                span 
                                    img(src="images/home/linkedin.png")
                            div.col-lg-4 
                                span.Copyright Copyright Â® 2023 Company All rights Reserved
                            div.col-lg-4 
                                span.Quixy_Logo powered by 
                                    img(src="images/home/Quixy_Logo.png")
                            
                        
                    
                
            
        